These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
City: berlin, marseilles
Music-Genre: techno, gospel
1. Music-Genre:techno is in an even position##4
2. Music-Genre:gospel == City:marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| City   | marseilles | berlin |
| Music-Genre     | gospel    | techno   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Flower: daffodil, rose
Nationality: turkish, australian
1. Nationality:turkish is in an odd position##4
2. Flower:rose is on the left of Flower:daffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Flower   | rose | daffodil        |
| Nationality      | turkish  | australian |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
Birthday: july, april
Color: white, ebony
1. Color:white is in an odd position##4
2. Birthday:april is on the left of Birthday:july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Birthday   | april    | july |
| Color   | white | ebony |

